{"tid":491423,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"電競用腳侮辱中國選手 韓國主播被判終身禁賽","createTime":"2017-12-06T13:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T13:06:37.000Z","uid":22633,"like":667,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"44548675f1903f2a2b2d0edb59ff22e5d60d3c94","tid":491423,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:30:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/138869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F138869&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=069cf218\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/138869</a><br />\n<br />\n在美國洛杉磯舉辦ZCUP MASTERS索泰杯《星海爭霸》重製版錦標賽，內地前星海選手羅賢（Legend）殺入決賽，卻被韓國選手Larva打贏，對方領先後還用「腳」打鍵盤，引起網友熱議，最終更被主辦單位判終身禁賽。<br />\n<br />\n內地星海老冠軍羅賢帶著他的鍵盤滑鼠進入決賽，卻被韓國星海主播Larva打爆。比賽中，Larva確定自己取得優勢後，開始「雙手交叉打比賽」、「閉眼玩」、「躺著玩」，甚至「用腳玩」，開始不斷賣弄自己，羞辱對手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/212837_d62d24edc139e9a71195c67544908ba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F212837_d62d24edc139e9a71195c67544908ba6.jpg&h=6575bb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓仔呢舖真係花式撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34131ee415ede5a10ee6d2874e6eb4e210cd4731","tid":491423,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275d0b69412903b15d83e9b1a8632a8ed2b65827","tid":491423,"uid":62950,"like":506,"dislike":35,"score":471,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"唔理係咪韓狗先啦<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔覺咁樣花式玩打比賽有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g